release_note: Bug fix: Fixed app crashing while attempting to choose an image when creating a new category.
EveryQuote version 4 the latest version of the popular quote organizer comes equipped with sleek new design and advanced quote adding features to inspire users like never before.

Added category designations: Books People and Topics. Mark books completed. All quotes get background images automatically for fast easy sharing. All new Discover tab with search features to find any quote you want when you need it. Instantly share to Instagram and text messages either as text or image. Removed social networking aspect of the app. All quotes are save offline on your own device. No profile data is stored. Must retrieve quotes by 12 31 2022 all data including profile data will be deleted 1 1 2023.
Languages! The app is now available in 30 languages! Now you can store your favorite quote in your native tongue.

All new quote creation tools. All new searchable quote database. All new font selections. Ability to remove embedded ads throughout the app. Ability to share quotes with users and feed within the app. Ability to share quote categories with users and to the feed.
Explore quotes without creating a user account.
